<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">{{product.name}} &mdash; Effective {{date}}</p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>{{product.name}} ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, why, and how we handle it.</p>

  <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
  <p>{{product.dataCollectionSummary}}</p>

