  <p>We use collected data solely to provide and improve {{product.name}}. We do not sell personal data to third parties.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Storage</h2>
  <p>{{product.dataStorageSummary}}</p>

  <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>{{product.thirdPartySummary}}</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>

  <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>{{product.childrenPrivacySummary}}</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy. Changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:{{product.contactEmail}}">{{product.contactEmail}}</a>.</p>
